Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.20,0:00:54.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,来い 船井　決着をつけよう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.35,0:00:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Funai!\NLet's finish this!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.80,0:00:59.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,残り５分　星５つの大勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.88,0:00:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We're left with five minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.78,0:00:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...to determine the winner\Nof those 5 stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.64,0:01:03.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,４時間に渡る
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.64,0:01:03.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,限定ジャンケンの死闘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.80,0:01:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The 4-hour Restricted Rock Paper\NScissors match is ending soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.31,0:01:06.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,決着の時 来る
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.39,0:01:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The time has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.01,0:01:08.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すべてをかけた最後の勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.17,0:01:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything depends\Non this final battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.11,0:01:14.11,kaiji-main-top,,0,0,0,,Iron Hammer
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.72,0:01:18.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんで負けると知っとって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.72,0:01:18.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,戦わなあかんねん
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.81,0:01:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll definitely lose,\Nso why should I waste my time?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.46,0:01:22.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかも星５つの勝負やて？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.46,0:01:22.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アホか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.65,0:01:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And 5 stars for the wager?\NAre you crazy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.29,0:01:24.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,忘れたんかい Ｘのこと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.44,0:01:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten about X?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.63,0:01:27.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,チョキ３枚 隠しとる奴は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.63,0:01:27.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,必ずおる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.76,0:01:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone must be hiding\Nthe 3 Scissors card.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.53,0:01:31.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,電光掲示板の数字が
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.53,0:01:31.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それを証明してくれとる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.86,0:01:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The scoreboard has\Nconfirmed that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.40,0:01:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Funai has a Rock card.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.40,0:01:36.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,船井の持つカードはグー１枚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.40,0:01:36.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジはグー31枚と
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.99,0:01:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji has 31 Rock, 33 Paper\Nand 2 Scissors cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.04,0:01:40.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,パー33枚 チョキ２枚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.04,0:01:40.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,チョキ３枚分の計算が合わない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.68,0:01:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They're short of Scissors cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.88,0:01:43.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり隠し持っているＸがいる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.03,0:01:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So, X is definitely hiding it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.88,0:01:47.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なのに何でおどれと わざわざ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.88,0:01:47.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,戦わなあかんのや
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.32,0:01:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should I play with you then?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.69,0:01:51.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ボケが！ひっこんどれ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.00,0:01:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You creep, get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.12,0:01:54.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.25,0:01:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.53,0:01:58.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰や？もう ええやろ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.53,0:01:58.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう時間切れや
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.74,0:01:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?\NThat's enough already!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.15,0:02:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Time is running out.\NThere's no time for bargains.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.20,0:02:02.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,駆け引き 打っとる時やない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.20,0:02:02.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出て来い Ｘ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.70,0:02:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Show yourself, X!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.57,0:02:06.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どいつや どいつ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.62,0:02:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop hiding! Come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.27,0:02:10.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ま おどれが持っとるのは 戦えば
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.27,0:02:10.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負けると分かっとるチョキやから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.47,0:02:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We all know that X's Scissors\Nwill fail him if he fights.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.98,0:02:14.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そう たやすう名乗られへんのは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.98,0:02:14.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分からんでもない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.22,0:02:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand why\Nyou're afraid to give in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.45,0:02:16.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,せやけど もう時間がないんや
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.62,0:02:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But time's not on our side!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.75,0:02:19.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから おどれに有利な
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.75,0:02:19.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,条件をつけようやないか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.92,0:02:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'll offer you something\Nto your advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.68,0:02:23.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本来やったら 俺のグーに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.68,0:02:23.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おどれのチョキは必ず負ける
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.98,0:02:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Technically, my Rock\Nwill beat your Scissors.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.29,0:02:26.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし それをチャラにしたる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.29,0:02:26.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.42,0:02:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But now, I'm going to\Nmake it even!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.71,0:02:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of that, I'll give you\Nenough stars to save your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.59,0:02:31.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,星を 生き残れる分の星をやるで！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.83,0:02:34.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どや　文句あらんやろ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.83,0:02:34.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,破格の話や
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.00,0:02:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.69,0:02:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an extraordinary offer!\NWith this, you'll survive...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.83,0:02:38.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これで おどれは生き残る
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.83,0:02:38.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本望やろ Ｘ？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.01,0:02:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your wish, right, X?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.47,0:02:42.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ出てこい 出てこいや Ｘ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.56,0:02:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.03,0:02:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Show yourself, X!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.72,0:02:58.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,時が流れる　船井の熱弁むなしく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.72,0:02:58.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰も名乗りをあげない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.87,0:02:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The clock ticked away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.72,0:02:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody answered Funai.\NNobody identified himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.82,0:03:02.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どういうこっちゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.82,0:03:02.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カードを残したら終わりっちゅう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.98,0:03:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.90,0:03:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You know the rule. If you still\N have cards left, it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.39,0:03:06.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ルールを知らんわけでもないやろ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.39,0:03:06.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何で名乗り出んのや
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.98,0:03:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What's stopping you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.07,0:03:13.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,船井 いい加減 気がつけよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.19,0:03:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Funai, enough of this nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.04,0:03:17.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この限定ジャンケン
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.04,0:03:17.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その中盤でのアクシデント
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.27,0:03:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember the accident\Nthat occurred...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.19,0:03:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...in the middle of the Restricted\NRock Paper Scissors game?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.48,0:03:21.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アクシデント？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.48,0:03:21.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,異例の措置
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.62,0:03:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.36,0:03:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The exceptional actions...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.78,0:03:25.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,別室に連れて行かれた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.78,0:03:25.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ある男のこと
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.96,0:03:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...taken against the guy\Nwho broke the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.52,0:03:28.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何のことや
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.69,0:03:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.02,0:03:30.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,別室へ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.02,0:03:30.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,連れて行かれたっちゅうことは
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.35,0:03:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who had lost their stars\Nwill be taken to the other room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.42,0:03:33.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,星を失った奴のことか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.33,0:03:37.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも異例って… 異例…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.55,0:03:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's the exceptional action?\NExceptional...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.96,0:03:42.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この男は余分なカードを
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.96,0:03:42.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,トイレに捨て流した
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.10,0:03:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This man flushed his\Nexcess cards down the toilet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.70,0:03:45.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最初に言ったはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.92,0:03:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We've warned you from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.07,0:03:48.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そういう行為は
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.07,0:03:48.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一切 認めていないと
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.29,0:03:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We will not tolerate such actions!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.31,0:03:52.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カードの破棄は 破棄は
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.38,0:03:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He destroyed his cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.44,0:03:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.92,0:04:04.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうさ　あの時トイレに
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.92,0:04:04.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,破棄されたチョキ３枚は
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.10,0:04:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.60,0:04:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The destroyed cards were not\Nreflected on the scoreboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.22,0:04:07.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,電光掲示板に
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.22,0:04:07.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カウントされていねえのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.13,0:04:11.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり Ｘなんていねえんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.41,0:04:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So this means that\Nthere's no X at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.13,0:04:13.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これでお前は
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.13,0:04:13.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負けると分かっていても
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.45,0:04:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll lose. But then again, you\Nhave no choice but to fight me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.63,0:04:17.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カードを使い切るため
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.63,0:04:17.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺と戦うしかねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.50,0:04:21.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ 来な 船井
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.50,0:04:21.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,文字どおり最終戦だ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.89,0:04:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, Funai!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.92,0:04:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the final match.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.81,0:04:29.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は俺と戦い 吐き出す
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.81,0:04:29.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,詐欺と卑劣で蓄えたその星を！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.96,0:04:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We will fight and\Nyou'll hand them over!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.59,0:04:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The stars you amassed\Nby deception and fraud!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.48,0:04:34.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何てことや　残り４分
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.60,0:04:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn... only 4 minutes left.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:40.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あと ひとかきか ふたかきで
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:40.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,手が届くっちゅうのに
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.26,0:04:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so close to getting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.76,0:04:49.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,抱きつかれた　溺死寸前の３人に
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.02,0:04:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But 3 men who were going\Nto drown grabbed him tightly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.04,0:04:54.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クソッ クソッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn, darn, darn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.47,0:04:58.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,時間がねえんだ　ちゃっちゃと
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.47,0:04:58.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,済まそうぜ 星５つの勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.58,0:04:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have time,\Nlet's settle this once and for all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.15,0:04:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A 5 star bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.64,0:05:01.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,落ち込むのは その後にしてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.79,0:05:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Feel free to be\Ndepressed afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.08,0:05:04.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ来い 船井　勝負だ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.29,0:05:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it on, Funai! Let's start!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.83,0:05:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Who are you trying to kid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.48,0:05:07.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふざけろ！調子に乗んな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.92,0:05:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so arrogant!\NYour fate's just the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.15,0:05:10.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,首が絞まっとんのは
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.15,0:05:10.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前も同じやろ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.06,0:05:13.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やのに主導権を取ったような口で
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.06,0:05:13.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,星５つの勝負や？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.24,0:05:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You want a 5 star bet?! Quit acting\Nlike you have the upper hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.93,0:05:16.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無茶もたいがいにせえ アホか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.24,0:05:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Know your limits, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.39,0:05:19.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいとこ３つやろ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.39,0:05:19.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それで８個になる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.58,0:05:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,3 stars are sufficient.\NYou'll have eight then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.70,0:05:22.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あと１つは有り金はたいて買え
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.83,0:05:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Use your money to buy the last\None! You'll survive anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.07,0:05:26.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それで生き残れる　やのに
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.07,0:05:26.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それ以上望むやなんて言語道断
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.81,0:05:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're being plain greedy\Nto bargain for more!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.84,0:05:30.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,強欲も甚だしい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.84,0:05:30.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３つ　３つや カイジ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.03,0:05:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my final word!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.77,0:05:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,3 stars... 3 stars, Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:38.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,寝ぼけるなよ 船井　５つだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:38.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それ以外 一切 受け付けない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.92,0:05:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up, Funai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.67,0:05:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's 5 stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.00,0:05:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't accept anything less.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.30,0:05:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.32,0:05:41.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.32,0:05:41.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当然の話さ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.89,0:05:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.35,0:05:46.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,100パーセント勝てる勝負に
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.35,0:05:46.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,限界まで はるのは当たり前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.68,0:05:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If you know you're winning, you'll\Nput everything on the line too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.06,0:05:49.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,状況考えろ　もたもたしとって
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.06,0:05:49.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,時間切れになったら
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.27,0:05:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.82,0:05:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have much time\Nand if you drag things,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.69,0:05:53.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,目も当てられへんやろ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.69,0:05:53.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから今は手打ち
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.98,0:05:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,everything will be over!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.97,0:05:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to compromise!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.30,0:05:58.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,譲り合うんや
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.30,0:05:58.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざれ言も休み休み言えよ クズ野郎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.49,0:05:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut the nonsense, you scum!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.14,0:06:02.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちは ここまで徹底的に
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.14,0:06:02.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奪い合ってきたんじゃねえか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.37,0:06:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't we risk everything\Nto come this far?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.01,0:06:07.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それを言うに事欠いて譲り合い？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.01,0:06:07.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ぬかすな　恥を知れ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.34,0:06:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's up with all\Nthese compromising?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.09,0:06:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop all this!\NWhere's your pride?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.25,0:06:11.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪党なら最後まで悪党でいろよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.39,0:06:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're a scoundrel,\Nthen act like one till the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.02,0:06:13.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいんか？そこの２人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.22,0:06:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You two are okay with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.92,0:06:17.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジに成り行きを任せとったら
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.92,0:06:17.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このまま時間切れ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.11,0:06:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If you leave things up to Kaiji,\Nyou're wasting your time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.42,0:06:19.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全員 別室行きやぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.86,0:06:23.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,安心しろ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.86,0:06:23.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いざとなったら俺の星と
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.99,0:06:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.79,0:06:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,At the very least,\Nyou can take my stars...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.46,0:06:25.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,600万で星６個には到達する
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.60,0:06:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,...to get six stars\Nalong with the 6 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.96,0:06:29.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前らは それであがればいい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.96,0:06:29.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも それじゃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.17,0:06:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You can use it to get out of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.17,0:06:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.30,0:06:32.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさんは？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.30,0:06:32.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その場合…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.42,0:06:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take him down with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.04,0:06:34.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺はこのクズと心中する
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.94,0:06:38.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つ 強がんなや
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.94,0:06:38.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,強がりじゃないさ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.18,0:06:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Stop fooling around!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.04,0:06:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Who says that I am?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.71,0:06:40.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前から５つ星を取ろうと
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.88,0:06:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't get your 5 stars,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:43.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,取れずにこのまま
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:43.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,沈むことになろうと
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.09,0:06:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll still sink.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.52,0:06:46.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どっちに転んでも同じことなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.66,0:06:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So either way, it's the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.42,0:06:49.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,同じこと？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.68,0:06:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.19,0:06:53.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,同じこと？何や どういうことや
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.41,0:06:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.10,0:06:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? What's his point?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.49,0:07:00.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あと３分 あと３分や
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.49,0:07:00.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな時に何を謎めいたことを
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.62,0:06:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,3 minutes left... Only 3 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.70,0:06:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is he acting so\Nmysterious at this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.73,0:07:04.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつら あと３分で
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.73,0:07:04.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カードを消耗しきれんのか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.91,0:07:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they planning to get rid of\Ntheir cards in 3 minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.90,0:07:09.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奴らが持ってるカードは
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.90,0:07:09.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,66枚やから
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.05,0:07:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They have 66 cards\Nbetween them...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.74,0:07:13.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,66枚？え…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.97,0:07:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,66 cards...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.92,0:07:23.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ　俺たちのカードは66枚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.92,0:07:23.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前と１戦すると65枚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.10,0:07:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. We have 66 cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.97,0:07:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,After this match,\Nwe will have 65 cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.66,0:07:28.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仲間内で消耗しようとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.66,0:07:28.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,必ず１枚残る
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.87,0:07:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if they want to play among\Nthemselves, there'll be 1 card left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.03,0:07:30.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３枚破棄というアクシデントが
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.08,0:07:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Due to the accident,\Nthe number of cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.30,0:07:34.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本来 割り切れるはずの
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.30,0:07:34.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カードの数を割り切れなくした
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.44,0:07:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...that was supposed to be\Ndivisible is now indivisible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.17,0:07:39.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり カイジ 古畑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.17,0:07:39.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,安藤の中から必ず１人は落ちる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.48,0:07:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This means one of\Nthe 3 guys will surely fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.91,0:07:45.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.91,0:07:45.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,安心しろ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.16,0:07:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- Kaiji...!\N- Kaiji...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.29,0:07:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax, I'll fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.41,0:07:48.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が落ちる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.65,0:07:51.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が船井を抱いて落ちる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.79,0:07:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm bringing Funai along!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.55,0:07:55.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カ カイジ…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.67,0:07:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,K-Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.19,0:08:01.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ムダや　死を負うと決した者に
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.19,0:08:01.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どんな説得もムダ…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.44,0:07:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good. When someone\Nis determined to die,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.06,0:08:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no persuading him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.09,0:08:05.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,船井は屈服　屈服せざるをえない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.33,0:08:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Funai gives up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.37,0:08:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He has no choice\Nbut to surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.56,0:08:09.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジの条件を飲み 星５つの勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.72,0:08:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He accepted Kaiji's conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.90,0:08:13.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,チェック　セット
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.02,0:08:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Check.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.98,0:08:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Set.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.51,0:08:15.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オープン
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.62,0:08:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.44,0:08:19.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当然 残るカードが
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.44,0:08:19.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グーと知られている船井は
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.48,0:08:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Funai loses since his remaining\Ncard was already revealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.18,0:08:23.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敗北　星５つを吐き出す
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.61,0:08:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He hands over the 5 stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.88,0:08:26.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やったー！カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.08,0:08:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- We did it!\N- Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.16,0:08:36.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジらは得た
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.16,0:08:36.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,土壇場で星を５つ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.36,0:08:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji and gang managed\Nto win the 5 stars!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.36,0:08:39.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,残り１分半　幕切れ寸前で
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.52,0:08:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They've finally obtained 9 stars!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.56,0:08:42.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ついに至った星９個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.72,0:08:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They have 1 and a half minutes left\N before the curtain closes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.50,0:08:45.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや 正確には星10個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.78,0:08:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Technically, they have 10 stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.27,0:08:48.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これで終えることができれば
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.27,0:08:48.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まさに快挙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.46,0:08:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If they can end it here,\Nit will be a great accomplishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.67,0:08:51.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だがカイジらが
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.67,0:08:51.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,残したカードは奇数
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.85,0:08:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,However, they have 65 cards left.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.58,0:08:53.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１人は落ちざるをえない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.74,0:08:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone has to fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.51,0:08:57.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.51,0:08:57.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,安心しろ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.80,0:08:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.73,0:08:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.80,0:08:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.05,0:08:59.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が落ちる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.24,0:08:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I will fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.75,0:09:05.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが ただ落ちるわけじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.75,0:09:05.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺はお前らに託して落ちるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.89,0:09:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,However, it's not that easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.57,0:09:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll entrust you with everything\Nbefore going down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.39,0:09:09.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,託す？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.39,0:09:09.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ　聞け
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.60,0:09:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Entrust?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.83,0:09:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.38,0:09:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.56,0:09:12.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は復活する
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.66,0:09:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall be restored back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.74,0:09:21.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺はお前らに
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.74,0:09:21.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,星を全部 預けて落ちる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I will give you all the stars now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.30,0:09:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, during the buy-sell period,\Nuse them to get me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.34,0:09:23.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前らは この後の売買タイムの時
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.98,0:09:28.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その星を使って 俺をあそこから
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.98,0:09:28.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,引き上げてくれればいい
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.12,0:09:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,K-Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.15,0:09:31.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん 可能なんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.15,0:09:31.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなこと
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.65,0:09:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.85,0:09:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the organisers will\Nallow that to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.89,0:09:35.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あいつらが星の売買で
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.89,0:09:35.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,救済されるっていうのは
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.22,0:09:37.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,船側も認めてると思うんですけど
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.88,0:09:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm unsure if it includes those\Nwho've been sent to the other room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.96,0:09:41.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが別室に落ちた人間にまで
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.96,0:09:41.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,及ぶんでしょうか？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.63,0:09:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.63,0:09:44.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大丈夫　及ぶ　及ぶはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.75,0:09:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It can be done, I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.90,0:09:49.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも もしそうじゃなかったら？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.90,0:09:49.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,売買は前回までで
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.91,0:09:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But... what if that's\Nnot the case?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.56,0:09:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What if the previous buy-sell\Nperiod was the last one?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.10,0:09:51.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今回からは
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.10,0:09:51.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ナシなんてことになったら？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.68,0:09:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Furuhata, we have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.74,0:09:55.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,古畑 他に手はねえのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.74,0:09:55.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.55,0:09:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.74,0:10:00.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのあたりの怪しさは
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.74,0:10:00.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺も重々 分かっちゃいるが
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.82,0:09:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that it's unsafe to\Nbet on something so dubious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.10,0:10:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Regardless of the reason,\Nit's our only choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.12,0:10:04.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,紙細工のような利でも
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.12,0:10:04.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう これに乗るしかねえんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.89,0:10:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.92,0:10:09.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.92,0:10:09.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,受け取れ　安藤 古畑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.77,0:10:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. Furuhata, Ando,\NI'm depending on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.33,0:10:11.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頼んだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.33,0:10:11.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もちろんっすよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.37,0:10:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.95,0:10:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You can count on us, Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.96,0:10:16.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,任せてください カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.96,0:10:16.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,必ず 必ず助けます
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.90,0:10:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We will surely save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.29,0:10:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.33,0:10:19.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほら　最後の勝負だ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.96,0:10:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the last match.\NUse this to defeat me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.77,0:10:23.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前はそのチョキで俺に勝ち
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.77,0:10:23.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この胸の星を受け取るんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.76,0:10:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and take this star.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.74,0:10:28.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして俺は垂れ尾のカードと共に
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.74,0:10:28.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いったん破滅する
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.84,0:10:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take the extra cards\Nwith me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.79,0:10:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and dispose them all at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.48,0:10:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.48,0:10:30.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.13,0:10:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Check...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.22,0:10:36.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,チェック　セット　オープン
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.74,0:10:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Set... Open.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.09,0:10:44.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジはゲーム終了後の星売買に
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.09,0:10:44.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生き残りを懸ける
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.17,0:10:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji places his hopes\Non the buy-sell period.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.33,0:10:48.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自らの命運を古畑と安藤に託した
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.36,0:10:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,As such, he places his life in\NFuruhata and Ando's hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.10,0:10:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the end of the Restricted\NRock Paper Scissors game.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.10,0:10:54.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして限定ジャンケンが終わった
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.67,0:10:57.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しばらく待機　その場を動くな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.81,0:10:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, don't move from\Nthis place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.58,0:11:03.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.69,0:11:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Move.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.77,0:11:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.85,0:11:05.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.27,0:11:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji... thank you!\NThank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.29,0:11:13.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん　ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.29,0:11:13.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ありがとうございます
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.16,0:11:16.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,必ず 必ず救い出しますから
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.17,0:11:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We will definitely...\Nsave you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.30,0:11:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.36,0:11:28.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジは感じた　古畑と安藤が
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.36,0:11:28.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とても遠くにいるような違和感
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.02,0:11:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji felt something then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.51,0:11:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He sensed that Furuhata\Nand Ando were very far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.04,0:11:32.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺はもしかしたら
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.04,0:11:32.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何かとんでもない間違いを…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.04,0:11:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I just make\Nan incredible mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.72,0:11:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Take them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.78,0:11:40.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,脱げ　着ているものを脱ぐんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.78,0:11:40.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すべて
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.88,0:11:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Take off everything,\Nall of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.46,0:11:51.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい 何だよ おい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.51,0:11:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.49,0:12:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,They are the people\Nwho were ruined...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.55,0:12:13.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,破滅　破綻者の巣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.74,0:12:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey kid, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.78,0:12:16.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,来なよ　そこの
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.79,0:12:19.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんた 助かる見込みが
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.79,0:12:19.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あるんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.87,0:12:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You're waiting to be saved, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.69,0:12:24.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,来な　ここが特等席
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.69,0:12:24.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,救われる者の席
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.78,0:12:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here.\NThese are VIP seats,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.43,0:12:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,for those who will be rescued.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.29,0:12:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So you will definitely\Nget out of here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.30,0:12:31.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,救われるって何か確信でも？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.90,0:12:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.97,0:12:37.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当たり前だ　でなきゃ誰が
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.97,0:12:37.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな損な役回りするか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, who would take up\Nsuch a thankless role?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.41,0:12:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Frankly, I had no choice\Nbut to take this role...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.47,0:12:41.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もっとも俺はシャバでの
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.47,0:12:41.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,借金がでかすぎるんで
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.34,0:12:47.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この役回りも仕方ないって言えば
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.34,0:12:47.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仕方ないんだけどな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.48,0:12:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...because I was too\Ndeep in debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.06,0:12:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's tunnelling...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.08,0:12:51.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,透視か
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.08,0:12:51.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢透視｣　この部屋とフロアが
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.43,0:12:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Tunneling... Those who've\Nbeen here would know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.32,0:12:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a one-way magic mirror\Nbetween this room and the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.39,0:12:54.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,マジックミラーで
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.39,0:12:54.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仕切られてると知るリピーターが
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.66,0:12:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,One of their comrades\Nis sent here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.66,0:12:59.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仲間を１人送り込み
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.66,0:12:59.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,対戦相手のカードを盗み見させる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.60,0:12:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...to peek at their\Nopponents' cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.73,0:13:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The number of knocks is a code\Nto notify their comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.83,0:13:05.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あとはミラーを打つ回数などで
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.83,0:13:05.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仲間に教えればいい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.10,0:13:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Two groups used this method\Nand they both succeeded.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.13,0:13:10.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今回 この手を使った者は
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.13,0:13:10.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２組あり 共に成功した
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.34,0:13:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the groups was Okabayashi\Nand his comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.34,0:13:13.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１組はこの岡林とその仲間たち
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.80,0:13:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And the other group would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.88,0:13:16.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そしてもう１組は
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.23,0:13:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,A man named Sakai\Npersuaded Ishida...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.28,0:13:26.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,サカイという男に説得され
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.28,0:13:26.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この戦略を受け入れた石田である
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.56,0:13:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,...into adopting this strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.87,0:13:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... You're the kid who\Nborrowed 10 million, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.02,0:13:30.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１千万 借りてた子だね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.02,0:13:30.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確か カイジ君…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.31,0:13:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Kaiji, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.54,0:13:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.59,0:13:34.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.59,0:13:34.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんたも助けてもらえる約束で
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.76,0:13:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're here because they\Npromised you'll be free, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.43,0:13:36.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,落ちた口かい？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.43,0:13:36.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.61,0:13:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.37,0:13:39.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そりゃ よかったなあ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.37,0:13:39.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.43,0:13:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.57,0:13:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But still... I don't know if\Nbeing here is a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.84,0:13:42.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この状態をよかったと
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.84,0:13:42.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言うべきかどうか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.57,0:13:45.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我々はここを
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.57,0:13:45.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出ることができるんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.60,0:13:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.\NWe won't be here long.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.77,0:13:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we're free,\Nour debts will be cancelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.81,0:13:49.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出さえすれば借金が帳消し
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.81,0:13:49.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やり直すことができる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.96,0:13:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We can start afresh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:52.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう取り立てに
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:52.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,苦しむことはないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.75,0:13:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Never again will the\Nloansharks torment us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.65,0:13:56.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君 我々はやり直せるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.72,0:13:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji... we'll start afresh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.01,0:13:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We can start all over again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.02,0:13:59.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やり直せるんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.35,0:13:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.76,0:14:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All thanks to Sakai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.79,0:14:02.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これもサカイさんのおかげだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.69,0:14:06.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの人が俺に
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.69,0:14:06.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生き残りの道を指してくれたから
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.76,0:14:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He showed me how to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.82,0:14:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He promised to get six stars,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.86,0:14:11.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,星を６つ稼いで
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.86,0:14:11.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺を引き上げてくれるって
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.75,0:14:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and use them to get me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.77,0:14:14.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ分からないって
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.94,0:14:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's still uncertain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.17,0:14:18.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ船側にお膳を
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.17,0:14:18.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひっくり返される可能性がある
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.20,0:14:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The organisers might\Njust surprise us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.47,0:14:21.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今回に限り売買はない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.47,0:14:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,For instance, maybe there\Nwill be no buy-sell...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.08,0:14:23.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんてこと
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.08,0:14:23.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなこと
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.06,0:14:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no way...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.86,0:14:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonegawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.92,0:14:32.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.92,0:14:32.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,４時間が経過し
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.59,0:14:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,4 hours have passed,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.29,0:14:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the Restricted Rock Paper Scissors\Ngame has ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.32,0:14:35.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,限定ジャンケン そのすべてが終了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.89,0:14:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the floor is still\Nfull of people with 1 or 2 stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.96,0:14:39.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが見たところ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.96,0:14:39.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,星１つ ２つの者たちが
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.53,0:14:41.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このフロアにあふれている
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.89,0:14:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't send all of you\Nto the other room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.93,0:14:44.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その者たちを
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.93,0:14:44.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全員別室へ送るというのは
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.83,0:14:50.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あまりに忍びない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.83,0:14:50.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何とか数名でも救いたい 何とか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.55,0:14:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If possible, we'd like to save\Nat least a few of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.01,0:14:52.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこで検討を重ねた結果
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.06,0:14:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we've come to\Na conclusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.81,0:14:57.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,特例として星売買の機会を
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.81,0:14:57.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,急きょ設けることにした
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.84,0:14:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You can buy and sell\Nthe stars as a special exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.05,0:15:01.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,売買で星３つになれば救済する
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.07,0:15:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You will need to get\N3 stars in order to be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.88,0:15:04.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よし　助かる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.90,0:15:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! I'm saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.21,0:15:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! They can\Npick me out with this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.22,0:15:11.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やった！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.22,0:15:11.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これで向こうから指名できる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.80,0:15:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be saved...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.83,0:15:14.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,助かる！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.83,0:15:14.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よかった
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.82,0:15:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.16,0:15:16.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本当は少し不安だったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.17,0:15:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly I was afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.56,0:15:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I feared that I wouldn't\Nbe saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.60,0:15:20.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ギリギリで
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.60,0:15:20.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひっくり返されるんじゃないかと
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.93,0:15:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's all in Sakai's\Nhands to save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.00,0:15:22.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あとはサカイさんが
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.00,0:15:22.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,救ってくれるのを待つだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.84,0:15:27.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- What is it? \N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.16,0:15:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you laughing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.21,0:15:32.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何で笑ってんの あんた
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.21,0:15:32.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すまん　気に障ったら勘弁な
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.21,0:15:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry if I've offended you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.55,0:15:35.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ あまりに
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.55,0:15:35.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おかしかったもんで
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.62,0:15:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.45,0:15:39.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おかしい？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.45,0:15:39.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのサカイって奴はどこに？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.64,0:15:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.49,0:15:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's that Sakai fellow?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:45.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,え？どこ… どこって
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:45.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,多分トイレにでも
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.17,0:15:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's... Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.61,0:15:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he's in the washroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.99,0:15:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, when will you\Nrealise the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.09,0:15:47.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どこまで おめでたいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.96,0:15:51.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのサカイってのは
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.96,0:15:51.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今 ビールでも飲んでるんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.18,0:15:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This Sakai is probably\Nenjoying a beer right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.83,0:15:56.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,上で
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.83,0:15:56.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,う 上？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.89,0:15:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.22,0:15:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.13,0:15:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.27,0:15:58.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.66,0:16:16.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最後にお膳をひっくり返すのは
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.71,0:16:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It goes to show that\Nlast minute surprises...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.79,0:16:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...don't come from\Nthe organisers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.89,0:16:19.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何も船側だけじゃないってことさ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.63,0:16:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Your buddy had 6 stars, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.66,0:16:24.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さっきあんた 相棒は
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.66,0:16:24.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,６つ星を稼いだって言ったな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You should have known from the\Nstart that they couldn't save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.03,0:16:28.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そもそも それじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.03,0:16:28.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最初から救われない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.24,0:16:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That Sakai's been here, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.27,0:16:30.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,サカイってのは
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.27,0:16:30.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,リピーターなんだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.66,0:16:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Repeaters like him need 4 stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.67,0:16:34.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,リピーターが生き残るには
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.67,0:16:34.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,星は４つ必要なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.47,0:16:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,4 stars?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.54,0:16:37.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,４つ…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.54,0:16:37.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奴がこいつを救おうと思ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.72,0:16:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If Sakai wanted to save him,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.91,0:16:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,he needs to cough up his\Nown money to buy another star.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.91,0:16:42.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自腹を切って もう１つ星を
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.91,0:16:42.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仕入れなきゃならんってこと
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.29,0:16:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would want to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.35,0:16:45.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この船で誰がそんなことするかい
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.19,0:16:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's natural to be betrayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.22,0:16:49.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,裏切られるのが当たり前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.22,0:16:49.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ま 仮にそのサカイってのが
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.53,0:16:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if Sakai has 7 or 8 stars,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.69,0:16:54.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,星を７つ ８つ稼いでいたとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.69,0:16:54.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,切られることに変わりはない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.00,0:16:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,he would still betray him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.06,0:16:56.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奴から見たら
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.06,0:16:56.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつは ただの捨て駒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.18,0:16:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,In his eyes,\Nthat guy is only a pawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.97,0:17:00.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よせ　いい加減にしろ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.06,0:16:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, that's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.36,0:17:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that it's partly\Nhis fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.37,0:17:03.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.37,0:17:03.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのサカイって奴の言いなりで
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.07,0:17:07.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本当の人間関係を築かなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.07,0:17:07.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このおっさんにも非はあるけど
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.10,0:17:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,...to follow Sakai blindly and not\Ndevelop a true relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.08,0:17:09.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だからって
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.08,0:17:09.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そういう言い方はやめろ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.19,0:17:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But stop adding fuel\Nto the fire, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.79,0:17:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down. Fine, I'll be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.81,0:17:14.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,怒るなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.81,0:17:14.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やめろと言われりゃやめるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.02,0:17:16.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死んだ犬を蹴飛ばしても仕方ない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.15,0:17:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't bother with\Nsomeone like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.74,0:17:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm concerned about\Nsomething.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.75,0:17:20.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ １つ気になるのは
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.14,0:17:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You mentioned true relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.16,0:17:24.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんた
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.16,0:17:24.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本当の人間関係って言ったけど
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.03,0:17:26.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本当のって 何？それ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.08,0:17:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you define... true?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.62,0:17:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.73,0:17:30.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何って… 一緒に
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.15,0:17:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We went through the game together,\Nand I believe that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.67,0:17:32.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この限定ジャンケンを
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.67,0:17:32.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,乗り越えてきて その…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.98,0:17:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We've passed the stage of\Nbetraying or being betrayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.00,0:17:38.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,裏切るとか裏切らないとか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.00,0:17:38.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そういうことを超えた
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.66,0:17:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,There's trust and then\Nthere's the bond...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.71,0:17:44.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信頼っていうか絆…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.71,0:17:44.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何それ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.34,0:17:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.01,0:17:46.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死ぬな お前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.12,0:17:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.14,0:17:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.24,0:17:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to be saved,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.25,0:17:51.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここから
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.25,0:17:51.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,引き上げてもらおうと思ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.02,0:17:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,you must have money\Nlike me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.02,0:17:53.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺みたいにカネを抱いて落ちるか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.90,0:17:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,or have some treasure hidden\Nin the corrupt world outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.92,0:17:57.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シャバに強力な
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.92,0:17:57.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お宝でも隠していて
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.20,0:17:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the only passport\Nto being saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.26,0:18:00.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,助けざるをえないという
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.26,0:18:00.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,状況しかない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.08,0:18:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite that, you're talking\Nabout meaningless things...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.13,0:18:03.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なのに お前ときたら
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.13,0:18:03.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絆とか信頼とか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.77,0:18:06.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,訳の分からない寝ぼけたことを
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.78,0:18:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,...such as bonds and trust...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.93,0:18:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, shut up, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.00,0:18:08.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,黙れ 黙れ 黙れ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.30,0:18:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know how far Furuhata,\NAndo and I have gone through!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.34,0:18:12.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は何も知らないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.34,0:18:12.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺と古畑と安藤がくぐってきた
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.71,0:18:16.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここまでの地獄を
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.71,0:18:16.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絆を 信頼を
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.35,0:18:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Our bond, our trust!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.15,0:18:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.21,0:18:19.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さて諸君　時間は10分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.81,0:18:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You have 10 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.80,0:18:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever fails to get 3 stars by\Nthe end of 10 minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.85,0:18:22.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この10分で
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.85,0:18:22.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,星３つに至らぬ場合は
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.75,0:18:25.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今度こそ別室へ行ってもらう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.75,0:18:25.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ あの…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.82,0:18:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,...will be sent to the other room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.58,0:18:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.93,0:18:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to save someone from\Nthe other room with 3 stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.99,0:18:30.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,星３つで別室の人を
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.99,0:18:30.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,復活させたいんですけど
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.69,0:18:34.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうぞご自由に
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.69,0:18:34.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ありがとうございます
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.74,0:18:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Please go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.91,0:18:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.50,0:18:38.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見たか　聞いたか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.52,0:18:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see that?\NDid you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.38,0:18:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They showed no sign of betrayal!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.43,0:18:43.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奴らには裏切ろうなんて気は
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.43,0:18:43.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,かけらもねえんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.23,0:18:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. What an\Nunexpected development.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.27,0:18:46.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なるほど　こりゃ予想外の展開だ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.47,0:18:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember, anything can happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.54,0:18:49.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし まだ分からない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.54,0:18:49.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ言うか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.54,0:18:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still not giving up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.38,0:18:55.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,では これより10分　始め
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.40,0:18:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well then. Your 10\Nminutes starts... now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.59,0:19:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sell it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.06,0:19:05.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,500万 500万！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.35,0:19:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sell it to me! Sell it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.33,0:19:09.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,売ってくれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.33,0:19:09.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,500万だ 500万！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.40,0:19:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sell it to me please!\N5 million, 5 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.67,0:19:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Ando, let's sell one!\NEven if we sold one,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.13,0:19:14.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,安藤 １つ売るぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.13,0:19:14.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１つ売っても３つは余る
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.13,0:19:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,we have 3 left.\NWe can still save Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.57,0:19:19.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさんは救える
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.57,0:19:19.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほら！500万の奴！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.64,0:19:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's for 5 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.34,0:19:26.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やった！やったぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.34,0:19:26.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これで上に上がれる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.79,0:19:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I can go up now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.55,0:19:29.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,売ってくれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.55,0:19:29.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,散れ！もうねえよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.64,0:19:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- Me too! Me too!\N- Go away! We have no more!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.95,0:19:33.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,残る３つは大切な仲間を
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.95,0:19:33.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,助けるための星だ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.17,0:19:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We need the last 3\Nto save someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.78,0:19:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no more left!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.82,0:19:38.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,他をあたんな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.82,0:19:38.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,離れろ　離れろよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.27,0:19:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Get lost... get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.13,0:19:40.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行けったら おい 行け！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.46,0:19:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Get lost, get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.20,0:19:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.31,0:19:57.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの 向こうの人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.31,0:19:57.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,救いたいんですけど
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.18,0:19:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to save someone there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.49,0:19:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Furuhata...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.51,0:19:59.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,古畑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.57,0:20:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The bond between comrades\Nthat has passed through death.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.65,0:20:08.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死をくぐり抜けた仲間の絆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.62,0:20:11.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ ついに生還
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.67,0:20:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, Kaiji is saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.96,0:20:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's him. This man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.00,0:20:18.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この人です　この人 助け…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.84,0:20:23.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言ったろ！売る星はもうねえって
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.97,0:20:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no more\Nstars left for sale!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.00,0:20:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Ando?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.04,0:20:29.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうした 安藤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.28,0:20:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.38,0:20:35.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ダメだ　この星もカネも
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.38,0:20:35.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,手放さない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.43,0:20:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let go of either\Nthe stars or the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.02,0:20:39.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,放したくない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.02,0:20:39.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何 言ってんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.03,0:20:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to let go...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.82,0:20:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.48,0:20:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We wouldn't be able\Nto save Kaiji then!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.55,0:20:41.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それじゃカイジさんが
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.55,0:20:41.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,救えないじゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.71,0:20:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.82,0:20:44.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,構わない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.50,0:20:55.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ あ あ あ 安藤！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.62,0:20:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Ando!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.40,0:21:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,At the very end,\Ndue to the betrayal of Ando,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.42,0:21:17.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最後の最後　命を託した仲間
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.42,0:21:17.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,安藤の裏切り
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.92,0:21:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,the comrade to whom\Nhe entrusted his life,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.85,0:21:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji regrets!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.86,0:21:20.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ 痛恨！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.41,0:22:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, Resurrection.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.48,0:22:45.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次回 ｢回生｣
